# StaySync â€” Complete 2-Week Project Plan

## Project Summary

**StaySync** is a unified Hotel Management System (HMS) for independent hotels and boutique resorts. It centralizes bookings, front-desk operations, housekeeping, billing/POS, and guest communications into a single real-time dashboard.

**Tech Stack:**
- **Backend:** PHP / Laravel (API) + MySQL
- **Frontend:** React.js (Vite) + Zustand (state management)
- **Real-time:** Laravel Broadcasting (Pusher or Soketi)
- **Email:** Laravel Mail (Mailtrap for dev, Mailgun/SES for prod)
- **Deployment:** Ubuntu VPS (DigitalOcean/AWS) or Laravel Forge

