#### **DAY 7 (Tuesday) â€” Dynamic Pricing + Guest Communications**

**You (Backend):**
- [ ] **Enhance the `PricingEngine`:**
  ```php
  class PricingEngine
  {
      public function calculateNightlyRate(RoomType $roomType, Carbon $date): float
      {
          // 1. Check for manual override
          $override = RateOverride::where('room_type_id', $roomType->id)
              ->where('date', $date->toDateString())
              ->first();

          if ($override) {
              return $override->override_rate;
          }

          $rate = $roomType->base_rate;

          // 2. Weekend surcharge (Fri/Sat)
          if ($date->isWeekend()) {
              $rate *= 1.15; // 15% weekend surcharge
          }

          // 3. Occupancy-based yield management
          $occupancyRate = $this->getOccupancyRate($date);
          if ($occupancyRate > 0.85) {
              $rate *= 1.20; // 20% surge when >85% occupied
          } elseif ($occupancyRate > 0.70) {
              $rate *= 1.10;
          }

          return round($rate, 2);
      }
  }
  ```
