## Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| Tape Chart takes too long | Use a simpler grid table (HTML table with colored cells) instead of a complex calendar library. Can always upgrade later. |
| Real-time is flaky | Fall back to polling (refetch every 30 seconds) if Pusher/broadcasting has issues. Implement both. |
| Dynamic pricing edge cases | Start with simple logic (base rate Ă— nights + weekend surcharge). Add occupancy-based pricing as a stretch goal. |
| Team member gets blocked | You (team lead) unblock immediately. Pair program for 30 mins. Reprioritize tasks. |
| Deployment issues | Have a Forge/Ploi account ready as backup. Use SQLite for quick demo if MySQL setup fails. |
| Scope creep | The POS, email, and reports are "nice to have." Core MVP = Rooms + Bookings + Tape Chart + Housekeeping. Cut from the bottom of the priority list. |

